_sText:
Just a small map for CSS. Made by GabrielPapaK, this is a fast killing map. Hope you enjoy!

Features:

Many Houses where people can hide.
Secret Area
Monitoring in secret area.

Install:
Extract the map file (many_houses_wcs.bsp), and the navigation file (many_houses_wcs.nav) to your Counter-Strike maps folder (Usually located here:C:\Program Files\steam\steamapps\***YOURNAMEHERE***\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps).

Author: GabrielPapaK

Time: 3 Hours

Story: Small map where Terrorist and Counter-Terrorist can fight. Face to face fighting. Close combat.
